---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout>

  <h1>About Forge70 Labs</h1>

  <p class="description">
      Practical AI, mobile applications, and automation tools
      engineered to solve real-world problems through reliability,
      simplicity, and decades of software engineering experience
  </p>


  <section>
  
    <h2>Our Story</h2>

    <p class="description">
        Forge70 Labs was founded on the belief that software should solve real problems. While technology evolves rapidly, thoughtful engineering, simplicity, and reliability remain timeless.
    </p>

  </section>

  <section>
  
    <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
  
    <p class="description">
        We believe the best software is:
    </p>
  
    <ul>
      <li>Reliable enough to earn trust</li>
      <li>Simple enough to understand</li>
      <li>Practical enough to solve real problems</li>
      <li>Built with quality from the very beginning</li>
    </ul>
  
    <p class="description">
      Technology should help people accomplish more—not become another obstacle.
    </p>
  
  </section>

  <section>
  
    <h2>What We Build</h2>
  
    <p class="description">
        Forge70 Labs develops:
    </p>
  
    <ul>
      <li>AI-powered applications</li>
      <li>Native mobile apps</li>
      <li>Intelligent automation tools</li>
      <li>Engineering-focused software solutions</li>
    </ul>
  
    <p class="description">
      Each product is engineered with long-term maintainability,
      usability, and quality in mind.
    </p>
  
  </section>

  <section>
  
    <h2>Looking Ahead</h2>
  
    <p class="description">
        Forge70 Labs is just getting started. As new products are developed, this site will become a place to explore the applications, ideas, and engineering practices behind them.
    </p>
  
  </section>

  <section>
  
    <h2>About the Founder</h2>
  
    <p class="description">
        Forge70 Labs was founded by an engineer with more than three decades of experience leading software development teams delivering production software. That experience shapes the company's commitment to reliability, thoughtful design, and engineering excellence.
    </p>
  
  </section>

</MainLayout>